      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to return to reliable operation. The exterior shows several dents, scratches, and clear coat failure, while the interior has heavy wear and some tears in the upholstery. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a noticeable leak, and the suspension feels quite loose, making it a project car or a candidate for parts. Please expect to invest in repairs if you intend to make this a daily driver.",
