      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the sophisticated driver. Maintained to a high standard of mechanical and cosmetic excellence, it delivers a balanced combination of performance and reliability. The interior remains remarkably well-preserved, complementing a powertrain that has been vetted for consistent operational integrity. A definitive choice for those seeking quality without compromise.",
