    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a linear power band peaking at its 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis is paired with the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Mechanical highlights include a documented VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity against high-torque loads. The suspension features upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers for precise turn-in and improved lateral stability. While the exterior displays honest wear from spirited road use, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. This is a mechanically sound example of BMW's M-division peak, ready for the next apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
