    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2018 BMW 530i in a classic Alpine White finish. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver, meticulously serviced at scheduled intervals. The exterior maintains a brilliant shine, though careful inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel, consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring Canberra Beige SensaTec upholstery. The seating is firm and supportive, with only light creasing on the driver's bolster. All electronics, including the 10.2-inch touchscreen, navigation, and dual-zone climate control, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the 2.0L TwinPower Turbo engine runs smoothly and quietly, with no leaks or warning lights. We recently performed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming that the brake pads and tires have significant life remaining. This car offers a balanced blend of luxury and performance for a buyer looking for a well-maintained vehicle that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
